Detailed Description

This is a namespace containing the original types and functions of the SESInstrument library.

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum SesNS::InstrumentStatus

Enumeration of the possible states for the SESInstrument library.

Enumerator:
Normal 

The library is functioning properly, and is currently idle.

Running 

An acquisition is currently running.

AcqError 

An acquisition was interrupted with an error.

NonOperational 

The library is not operational. Resetting may resolve the issue.

NotInitialized 

The SESInstrument library has not been initialized (the GDS_Initialize function has not been called).
